<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَأَمَةً وَأَمْرَدَ لِغَيْرِ مَأْمُونٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَتُضْمَنُ مُطْلَقاً:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- بِمِثْلِ مِثْلِيٍّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- وَقِيمَةِ غَيْرِهِ يَوْمَ تَلَفٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span class="c5"> لَا:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- إِنْ تَلِفَتْ بِاسْتِعْمَالٍ بِمَعْرُوفٍ؛ كَخَمْلِ مِنْشَفَةٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَلَا إِنْ كَانَتْ وَقْفاً؛ كَكُتُبِ عِلْمٍ، إِلَّا بِتَفْرِيطٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- وَعَلَيْهِ مُؤْنَةُ رَدِّهَا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ أَرْكَبَ مُنْقَطِعاً لِلهِ:</span> لَمْ يَضْمَنْ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَالغَصْبُ كَبِيرَةٌ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- فَمَنْ غَصَبَ كَلْباً يُقْتَنَى،<span class="c5"> أَوْ خَمْرَ ذِمِّيٍّ مُحْتَرَمَةً:</span> رَدَّهُمَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- لَا جِلْدَ مَيْتَةٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِتْلَافُ الثَّلَاثَةِ:</span> هَدَرٌ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنِ اسْتَوْلَى عَلَى حُرٍّ مُسْلِمٍ:</span> لَمْ يَضْمَنْهُ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>